Sung and composed by Sarit Dutta, this soulful melody beautifully captures the emotions of love, longing, and separation. The heartfelt lyrics by Dr. Uma Naveen Mehta paint a timeless picture of a betaab (restless) heart waiting for its beloved.

If you miss the charm of classic love songs, “Betaab Dil” will take you straight back to that nostalgic era of melody and emotion.

Through emotional latmiya and touching recitation, the grief of Ayyam e Fatima (sa) comes alive once again. The soulful verses of Fatima Yateem Ho Gai and the remembrance of Bagh e Fidak remind every believer of truth and sacrifice.
